Package: cada
Title: CADA Hypothesis Comparison for Between-Subject Data
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: c(
    person("Immanuel", "Stark", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "immanuel.stark@s2023.tu-chemnitz.de"),
    person("Codex", role = "ctb", comment = "mit freundlicher Unterstützung")
    )
Author: Immanuel Stark mit freundlicher Unterstützung von Codex
Maintainer: Immanuel Stark <immanuel.stark@s2023.tu-chemnitz.de>
Description: Provides one unified interface for comparing two competing
    hypothesized mean patterns in between-subject designs.
    The package supports bootstrap null distributions, normal approximations
    based on variance formulas, and a standardized CADA effect size for
    squared deviations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
